                          "heading": "Stage 1 — The Tunnel Gets Crowded",
                          "body": [
                              "Carpal tunnel syndrome occurs when the median nerve is compressed at the wrist.",
                              "This can cause numbness, tingling, burning, pain, weakness, or clumsiness."
