                  "label": "Strictly Medical",
                  "title": "Myopia Refractive Error & Distance-Focus Strain",
                  "sections": [
                      {
                          "heading": "Stage 1 — Eye Shape",
                          "body": [
                              "Nearsightedness is usually an optical focusing issue.",
                              "It is not caused by refusing to see the future. Cute, but no."
                          ]
                      },
                      {
                          "heading": "Stage 2 — Near Strain",
                          "body": [
                              "Distance blur can cause squinting, headaches, eye strain, and school/driving/work issues.",
                              "Prescription correction can reduce strain."
                          ]
                      },
                      {
                          "heading": "Stage 3 — Eye Exams",
                          "body": [
