              "witty": {
                  "label": "Comedic & Witty",
                  "title": "The Ground Microscope",
                  "paragraphs": [
                      "Your eyes are a microscope glued to the ground.",
                      "The gravel is crystal clear. The horizon is an impressionist painting with poor boundaries.",
                      "The optics need correction, not a sermon about perspective.",
                      "Get the eye exam. Wear the correction. Then maybe look up once in a while.",
                      "Widen the microscope or keep walking into the horizon like it personally offended you. Your choice."
