        "You have a sudden, blindingly severe headache or sudden loss of vision",
        "You experience a seizure, sudden confusion, or loss of consciousness"
      ],
      "schedule_care_if": [
        "You have frequent or progressively worsening headaches that interfere with sleep or work",
        "You experience occasional mild dizziness or subtle changes in coordination or memory",
        "You have persistent jaw pain or clicking that does not improve with stress reduction"
      ],
      "self_care_allowed_if": "Mild, familiar headaches or muscle tension may respond well to rest, hydration, and gentle massage.",
      "do_not_ignore": "Sudden neurological deficits or severe headaches must be immediately evaluated to rule out stroke, aneurysm, or other brain emergencies.",
      "disclaimer": "This app is for education and self-reflection only. It does not diagnose, treat, prevent, or cure disease. Seek professional medical care for diagnosis, treatment, medication decisions, or urgent symptoms."
    }
