          "self_care_allowed_if": "Meal timing, trigger tracking, upright posture after meals, smaller meals, and stress downshifting may support mild familiar reflux without red flags.",
          "do_not_ignore": "Heartburn can overlap with serious conditions, including heart-related symptoms. Chest pain and swallowing problems should not be treated as purely emotional or dietary.",
          "disclaimer": "This app is for education and self-reflection only. It does not diagnose, treat, prevent, or cure disease."
