        "Chest pain, pressure, squeezing, or fullness",
        "Pain radiating to the arm, shoulder, neck, jaw, or back",
        "Severe shortness of breath or difficulty breathing",
        "Fainting, dizziness, or lightheadedness",
        "Bluish tint to lips, face, or fingernails (cyanosis)",
        "Coughing up blood or pink-tinged sputum"
      ],
      "seek_immediate_care_if": [
        "You experience sudden chest pain or pressure, especially if spreading to the arm, jaw, or back",
        "You have severe shortness of breath, feel faint, or develop blue lips",
        "A rapid, irregular, or fluttering heartbeat occurs suddenly along with sweating, nausea, or profound weakness"
      ],
      "schedule_care_if": [
        "You experience occasional mild shortness of breath during normal daily activities",
        "You have persistent coughing, wheezing, or blood pressure readings that are consistently elevated",
        "You experience occasional heart palpitations or skipping beats that do not may contribute to dizziness or pain"
      ],
      "self_care_allowed_if": "Slow diaphragmatic breathing and relaxation techniques can help soothe mild, stress-induced chest tightness or hyperventilation.",
      "do_not_ignore": "Chest or breathing discomfort requires immediate medical attention to rule out life-threatening cardiac or pulmonary emergencies.",
      "disclaimer": "This app is for education and self-reflection only. It does not diagnose, treat, prevent, or cure disease. Seek professional medical care for diagnosis, treatment, medication decisions, or urgent symptoms."
    }
