        "Blistering, peeling, or painful shedding of skin or mucous membranes",
        "Rash or hives accompanied by difficulty breathing, wheezing, or facial/lip swelling",
        "Severe, sudden allergic reaction or hives that spread rapidly"
      ],
      "seek_immediate_care_if": [
