        "You notice red streaks spreading from a skin infection, or have a skin lesion that is extremely painful and hot",
        "Your skin begins to blister or peel off in large sheets"
      ],
      "schedule_care_if": [
        "You have a chronic skin condition (like eczema or psoriasis) that is flaring or not responding to treatment",
        "You notice changes in a mole’s size, shape, color, or borders (ABCDE melanoma check)",
        "You experience a persistent, unexplained rash or skin itching that interferes with sleep"
      ],
      "self_care_allowed_if": "Gentle, fragrance-free moisturizers and cool compresses can help calm minor, non-infectious skin irritation or stress flares.",
      "do_not_ignore": "Rapidly spreading skin changes or rashes with systemic symptoms can be signs of dangerous infections or severe allergic reactions.",
      "disclaimer": "This app is for education and self-reflection only. It does not diagnose, treat, prevent, or cure disease. Seek professional medical care for diagnosis, treatment, medication decisions, or urgent symptoms."
